{"tid":334872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【直擊貪心一家】強國一家五口呢招偷背囊 大肚失主：唔見200幾萬","createTime":"2017-07-25T06:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T09:28:57.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56a1942c0a9b626b6b837c324255d88fc41f538f","tid":334872,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170725/large/1500950223_87db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170725%2Flarge%2F1500950223_87db.jpg&h=a43985eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017年07月25日<br />\n山東德州驚現「貪心家族」！內地媒體今日報道，一名王姓孕婦上周五（21日）在快餐店吃飯，離開時忘記帶走放在座位上的背囊，結果被一家五口拿走了，店內閉路電視拍下了他們偷袋的全部過程。<br />\n<br />\n從閉路電視畫面可見，王女放下背囊吃飯，用完餐後起身離開，當時並沒有拿走背囊。她走後1小時，一名原本坐在鄰座的年長男子發現了她的背囊，看了一會後，便假裝隨意地坐到王女之前的座位上。隨後，他的4名家人來到快餐店，一家人坐下後迅速吃完飯，年長男子便拿着王女的背囊，若無其事地離開。<br />\n王女說，她的背囊裏最少有3,600元（人民幣‧下同）現金，連同信用卡、儲蓄卡等價值，總共有200多萬元。她說：「我包裏的現金，零的我不知道，整的是3,600，還有十多張信用卡、銀行儲蓄卡、還車貸的卡、在銀行貸款的卡，以及一些欠條，這些加起來將近200多萬。這個包沒有了後，我的日常生活及工作，都幹不了。我就是希望撿包的大爺看到這消息，能盡快把我的包送回來，我可以不追究你的任何責任。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170725/56998818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170725%2F56998818&d=Ynlc5qP%2BAAiannsWr8klek%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=eb67ed49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fchina%2F20170725%2F56998818&h=3ff22c6c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/china/20170725/56998818</a>"},{"pid":"2575cf6a36319da4aebc6680753fb8dfe55d0d10","tid":334872,"uid":37463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:28:30.000Z","msg":"原來唔見左既credi card limit都計數<br />\n唔見atm卡 就等於戶口既錢唔見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f19ebb69ed783ae29d548b9f0912407faf1b188","tid":334872,"uid":1059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb48dd062f1363280b9fc1247c53f45d24369352","tid":334872,"uid":81113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來唔見左既credi card limit都計數<br />\n唔見atm卡 就等於戶口既錢唔見埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n洗返白係靠呢招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40287254185adc10e32380eeeaf941db314ce9e2","tid":334872,"uid":8254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:30:25.000Z","msg":"兩邊都痴撚線"},{"pid":"d7ac836a07a4fa368e02d87548c2217a105ccbf1","tid":334872,"uid":48631,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:50:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老味唔唔見三千幾蚊畀佢吹撚到唔見二百萬,正一戇鳩蝗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599e5726ba2b6ec30216ac1c14e9e1902a970fa0","tid":334872,"uid":53121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"會唔會假左D<br />\n食完餐飯成個幾鐘都無發現自己唔記得拎背囊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e94a789bb71640f9207df2ab32e3ccd72b83ac1","tid":334872,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"呢個醒呀 3000蚊搵公安幫你？<br />\n含撚啦<br />\n而家吹到200萬 直頭上埋報<br />\n華春瑩今晚都會出來指責"},{"pid":"491d7f38b7bfadf8cb64091f31b0762b5b2f98e5","tid":334872,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T07:59:27.000Z","msg":"我唔見咗七五九卡